# Theme Rules

## Spacing Conventions

| Context | Class |
|---------|-------|
| Admin page padding | `p-4 md:p-6` (set by AdminShell) |
| Section vertical gap | `space-y-6` |
| Card internal padding | `p-4` or `p-5` |
| Button padding | `px-4 py-2.5` (standard) · `px-6 py-3` (large) |
| Form field gap | `space-y-4` |
| Icon + text gap | `gap-2` |
| Grid gap | `gap-4` or `gap-6` |

## Border Radius

| Element | Class |
|---------|-------|
| Inputs, buttons | `rounded-xl` |
| Cards, panels | `rounded-2xl` |
| Badges, pills | `rounded-full` |
| Avatar / circle | `rounded-full` |

## Typography Scale

| Use | Class |
|-----|-------|
| Page title | `text-2xl font-bold text-[#10231f]` |
| Section title | `text-xl font-bold text-[#10231f]` |
| Card title | `text-base font-semibold text-[#10231f]` |
| Body text | `text-sm text-[#10231f]` |
| Description / muted | `text-sm text-[#65736f]` |
| Label (uppercase) | `text-xs font-bold text-[#10231f] uppercase tracking-wide` |
| Faint / placeholder | `text-xs text-[#8a958f]` |

## Shadows

| Element | Class |
|---------|-------|
| Cards | `shadow-sm` |
| Primary action buttons | `shadow-md` |
| Dropdowns / modals | `shadow-xl` |

## Animations

- Loading skeleton: `animate-pulse`
- Spinner: `animate-spin`
- Interactive: `transition-colors` (always — never bare hover without transition)
- Modals: use framer-motion `AnimatePresence` — framer is installed, use it

## Admin Layout Structure

```
min-h-screen flex bg-[#f7f4ef]
  ├── AdminSidebar  (w-64, bg-white, border-r border-[#e5ded3], hidden md:flex)
  └── flex-1 flex flex-col
        ├── AdminHeader  (h-14, bg-white, border-b border-[#e5ded3])
        └── main  (flex-1 overflow-auto p-4 md:p-6)
```
